        .contents__content__category-list
          .contents__content__category-list__box
            .contents__content__category-list__box__name
              %h3.contents__content__category-list__box__name__new-item
                レディース新着アイテム
              = link_to "/", class: "contents__content__category-list__box__name__more" do
                もっと見る
